己的歷史嗎？」，播映兩片後便遭停播，亦令當地更警剔中國的文化滲透。<br />\n<br />\n由於聯署人數已經超過官方門檻，加上反華政黨在剛剛補選中大捷，令外國關注立場相當親華的執政黨政府如何回應，以及關注這鼓民間對華的批評聲音會否影響到日後韓國對華政策。<br />\n<br />\n聯署<br />\n<a href=\"https://www1.president.go.kr/petitions/597240\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww1.president.go.kr%2Fpetitions%2F597240&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqx8QbtkMcGro9tlpYeKwNq%2B0%3D&h=656435d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www1.president.go.kr/petitions/597240</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/TheKoreaHerald/status/1378941143186993152\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTheKoreaHerald%2Fstatus%2F1378941143186993152&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqx8QbtkMcGro9tlpYeKwNq%2B0%3D&h=5cb1026d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTheKoreaHerald%2Fstatus%2F1378941143186993152&h=eb32c543\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/TheKoreaHerald/status/1378941143186993152</a><br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://t.me/HKinternationalfront/654\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKinternationalfront%2F654&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqx8QbtkMcGro9tlpYeKwNq%2B0%3D&h=a8172bc1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKinternationalfront/654</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T03:32:03.000Z","msg":"仲有邊啲國家既人係唔反華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T03:38:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />邊次唔係小粉紅去撩鳩人..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T03:39:38.000Z","msg":"全世界人民公敵 中國"},{"pid":"11cc180d7f0d52c14c772ad5a5d743605d15fa7d","tid":2495056,"uid":264326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"591e90ba49e63f888544c661069c78d77c342b24","tid":2495056,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":